descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...a grid with two colors of randomly patterned blocks. Within the grid you will see some black 3x3 grids that are solid black.
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same as the input grid.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...Change all the black 3x3 grids to blue in the output grid.

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see... a grid filled randomly with a certain color and a black background.
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size... remains the same as the input grid.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to... FOR EACH identifiable 3x3 black grid within the random pattern, MAKE a 3x3 dark blue square if APPLICABLE and POSSIBLE
